  "text": "The structure of EMVDA was based on lessons learned from the EURHAVAC consortium [CITATION_1] . The EMVDA consortium actively cooperates with other global stakeholders in the field of malaria vaccine development, and in particular WHO. It participates in, and contributes to, agreed global coordination and harmonization efforts [102] .",
